
Overview of noun chop

The noun chop has 5 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                         
1. chop -- (the irregular motion of waves (usually caused by wind blowing in a direction opposite to the tide); "the boat headed into the chop")
2. chop -- (a small cut of meat including part of a rib)
3. chop -- (a jaw; "I'll hit him on the chops")
4. chop, chop shot -- (a tennis return made with a downward motion that puts backspin on the ball)
5. chop, chopper -- (a grounder that bounces high in the air)

